GET /tokens/{tokenAddress}.description: Retrieves comprehensive information about a specific token.

GET /tokens/{tokenAddress}/holders.description: Gets the top 100 holders for a specific token and the total amount

GET /tokens/{tokenAddress}/holders/top.description: Gets the top 20 holders for a token.

GET /tokens/{tokenAddress}/ath.description: Retrieves the all-time high price of a token (since the data API started recording).

GET /deployer/{wallet}.description: Retrieves all tokens created by a specific wallet with pagination support.

query_parameters.name: limit
query_parameters.description: Number of items per page (default: 250, max: 500)

GET /search.description: The /search endpoint provides a flexible search interface for pools and tokens with comprehensive filtering options and pagination.

query_parameters.name: limit
query_parameters.description: Number of items per page (default: 250, max: 500)

GET /tokens/trending.description: Gets the top 100 trending tokens based on transaction volume in the specified timeframe (default: past hour).

GET /tokens/trending/{timeframe}.description: Gets the top 100 trending tokens based on transaction volume in the specified timeframe (default: past hour).

GET /tokens/volume.description: Retrieves the top 100 tokens sorted by highest volume within the specified timeframe.

GET /tokens/volume/{timeframe}.description: Retrieves the top 100 tokens sorted by highest volume within the specified timeframe.

GET /tokens/multi/all.description: Gets an overview of latest, graduating, and graduated tokens (Pumpvision / Photon Memescope style).

GET /price.description: Gets price information for a single token.

query_parameters.name: priceChanges
query_parameters.description: Returns price change percentages up to 24 hours ago

GET /price/history.description: Gets historic price information for a single token.

GET /price/history/timestamp.description: Gets specific historic price information for a token at a given timestamp.

GET /price/history/range.description: Gets the lowest and highest price in a time range

GET /price/multi.description: Gets price information for multiple tokens (up to 100).

GET /wallet/{owner}.description: Gets all tokens in a wallet with current value in USD.

GET /wallet/{owner}/basic.description: Gets all tokens in a wallet with current value in USD (lightweight, non-cached option).

GET /wallet/{owner}/page/{page}.description: Retrieves wallet tokens using pagination with a limit of 250 tokens per request.

GET /wallet/{owner}/trades.description: Gets the latest trades of a wallet.

GET /wallet/{owner}/chart.description: Gets wallet portfolio chart data with historical values and PnL information.
notes: OHLCV data endpoint with customizable time intervals

GET /trades/{tokenAddress}/{poolAddress}.description: Gets the latest trades for a specific token and pool pair.
Gets the latest trades for a specific token, pool, and wallet address.

GET /chart/{token}.description: Gets OHLCV (Open, High, Low, Close, Volume) data for charts.

query_parameters.name: marketCap
query_parameters.description: Return chart for market cap instead of pricing

query_parameters.name: removeOutliers
query_parameters.description: Set to false to disable outlier removal, true by default

notes: OHLCV data endpoint with customizable time intervals

GET /chart/{token}/{pool}.description: Gets OHLCV (Open, High, Low, Close, Volume) data for charts.

query_parameters.name: marketCap
query_parameters.description: Return chart for market cap instead of pricing

query_parameters.name: removeOutliers
query_parameters.description: Set to false to disable outlier removal, true by default

notes: OHLCV data endpoint with customizable time intervals

GET /holders/chart/{token}.description: Gets token holder count data over time. Returns up to 1000 of the most recent data points.
notes: OHLCV data endpoint with customizable time intervals

GET /pnl/{wallet}.description: Gets Profit and Loss data for all positions of a wallet.

query_parameters.name: limit
query_parameters.description: Number of first buyers to return

GET /pnl/{wallet}/{token}.description: Gets Profit and Loss data for a specific token in a wallet.

GET /stats/{token}.description: Gets detailed stats for a token or token-pool pair over various time intervals.

GET /stats/{token}/{pool}.description: Gets detailed stats for a token or token-pool pair over various time intervals.

GET /events/{tokenAddress}.description: Gets raw event data for live processing. Returns binary data that needs to be decoded.

GET /events/{tokenAddress}/{poolAddress}.description: Gets raw event data for a specific token and pool. Returns binary data that needs to be decoded.

GET /credits.description: Gets the remaining API credits for your API key.
